title: How big can luxury resale get in Asia? - Vogue Business
summary: The secondhand market for luxury goods in Asia is gaining momentum after being overshadowed by the primary market. While resale platforms like The RealReal and Thredup have seen success in the West, the adoption in Asia has been slow due to concerns about counterfeiting and social status associated with new goods.
